{
  "stem": "23832.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in the ghetto that time, I think, in the beginning of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did I get?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started to put a wall with gates in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They built up a high wall, brick wall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on top, they built in broken glass.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and it was high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know how many feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when you wanted to get the other side, you cut yourself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they put a-- what do you call this-- a spotlight, a big one-- sometimes I see it here, and I shiver-- to lit up the whole ghetto so nobody would get through.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One time I said, Joseph, you see we going to perish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In that time, broke out-- I told you, the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that-- that typhus, that was the kind that it hits your brain.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you have no control-- physical control over your body.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was going there for the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the people wanted to leave so badly, those afflicted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they would give you this much money when you come for the night and watch them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't do anything for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In meantime, the institution received, I think, from Switzerland or somewhere else, some ampules, sort of like immunization.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they got only a few, very few, so that the institution would give like one ampule for two with another girl, and another nurse.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I don't believe it helped me not to become afflicted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think God helped me, because that was a tiny amount, wouldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we shared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I cannot forget one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When those, the Jewish called them militia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know what you call them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They called them [GERMAN], meaning in German, [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] order.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
